      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Auburn%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Just a few miles from Auburn, the Erie Canal opened in 1825, enabling cheap shipment of local goods.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
